is mengenai\u003Cb\u003E \u003Ca href=\"http:\/\/blogerbugis.blogspot.com\/2013\/08\/kumpulan-foto-foto-para-pejuang.html\"\u003Ekoleksi foto para pejuang\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/b\u003E, semoga dengan melihat foto foto diatas dapat mengingatkan kita kepada para pejuang kemerdekaan, mari mengisi kemerdekaan ini dengan hal hal yang dapat membangun Indonesia lebih Maju, \u003Cb\u003E\u003Ci\u003E\u003Cu\u003EJayalah Indonesiaku\u003C\/u\u003E\u003C\/i\u003E\u003C\/b\u003E.\u003Cdiv class=\"blogger-post-footer\"\u003EOriginal Posted By Creative Commons License \u003Ca href=\"http:\/\/blogerbugis.blogspot.com\/\"\u003EBlogger Bugis Media Info Terbaru\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/blogerbugis.blogspot.com\/feeds\/8759722440037587246\/comments\/default","title":"Poskan Komentar"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/blogerbugis.blogspot.com\/2013\/08\/kumpulan-foto-foto-para-pejuang.html#comment-form","title":"0 Komentar"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/7834997721307480080\/posts\/default\/8759722440037587246"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/7834997721307480080\/posts\/default\/8759722440037587246"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/blogerbugis.blogspot.com\/2013\/08\/kumpulan-foto-foto-para-pejuang.html","title":"Kumpulan Foto Foto Para Pejuang Kemerdekaan RI 1945"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"Anak Bugis"},"uri":{"$t":"https:\/\/plus.google.com\/110641781279489703680"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"32","height":"32","src":"\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/--wS7a59okoY\/AAAAAAAAAAI\/AAAAAAAAAg8\/poiT8YcRdy4\/s512-c\/photo.jpg"}}],"media$thumbnail":{"xmlns$media":"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/","url":"http:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-WWbeouRkasg\/UgoXwV87JmI\/AAAAAAAAAnQ\/tbmSVhR74vw\/s72